(90, 1, '2016-10-27 21:38:25', '2016-10-27 19:38:25', '<h1><img class="pull-right img-float-right-margin alignright" src="https://afeefa.de/translate/img/CallForTranslators.jpg" width="250" /></h1>\r\nWe, the team of <a href="http://afeefa.de/">Afeefa.de</a> started this translation initiative to translate the content on our website. And we invited other projects to join our group and share translation capabilities. We set up a <strong>TRANSLATION TOOL</strong> to get the work done.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://afeefa.de/">Afeefa.de</a> is a platform for connecting refugees, their supporters and the civil society. We offer content in up to 10 languages to boost independancy and self empowerment of refugees. <b>We need your help</b> to translate the content on a regular basis.\r\n\r\nWe''re joining forces with other projects to bring together translators and content into one place and to simplify things for everyone.\r\n<h3>How to</h3>\r\nOur <b>Guide for translators</b> explains how to use the translation tool.\r\n<h3>Join the team</h3>\r\nYou speak TIGRINYA, URDU, PERSIAN, PASHTO, FARSI, DARI, ARABIC, ENGLISH, RUSSIAN, SERBIAN or FRENCH ??\r\n\r\nIt would be great, if you felt like supporting our project and sharing your language skills! We''d love to see you using our new tool and start translating today! All projects connected to Afeefa.de will benefit immediately.\r\n\r\nYou would like to get involved <b>as a project</b> and benefit from the translation team? Good idea!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[phraseapp link]', 'Translate for Afeefa.de', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'translate', '', '', '2016-10-27 21:46:50', '2016-10-27 19:46:50', '', 0, 'http://about.afeefa.fx/?page_id=90', 0, 'page', '', 0),
